{"id": "art-308", "label": "Art. 308", "title": "Art. 308: Procedura audierii anticipate", "slug": "art-308", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_331347915\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1943\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_331347915\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 308:\nProcedura audierii anticipate </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1008201051\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1942\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1008201051\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Atunci când exist&#259; riscul ca persoana\nv&#259;t&#259;mat&#259;, partea civil&#259;, partea responsabil&#259;\ncivilmente sau un martor s&#259; nu mai poat&#259; fi audiat în cursul\njudec&#259;&#355;ii, procurorul poate sesiza judec&#259;torul de drepturi\n&#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i în vederea audierii anticipate a acestuia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1425357882\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1941\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1425357882\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i\nlibert&#259;&#355;i, dac&#259; apreciaz&#259; cererea întemeiat&#259;,\nstabile&#351;te de îndat&#259; data &#351;i locul audierii, dispunându-se\ncitarea p&#259;r&#355;ilor &#351;i subiec&#355;ilor procesuali principali. Când\naudierea are loc la sediul instan&#355;ei, aceasta se desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259;\nîn camera de consiliu.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1712810627\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1940\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1712810627\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Participarea procurorului este obligatorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_476069834\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1939\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_476069834\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Dispozi&#355;iile alin. (1)-(3) se aplic&#259; în mod\ncorespunz&#259;tor cu privire la audierea minorului martor sau parte\ncivil&#259;, precum &#351;i cu privire la audierea persoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate\ndac&#259;, în raport cu persoana acestora sau cu natura cauzei, procurorul\napreciaz&#259; c&#259; evitarea audierii repetate pe parcursul procesului este\nîn interesul acestora.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}